{"tid":1183202,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"攝影背包推薦","createTime":"2019-06-02T17:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:08:20.000Z","uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d0df37fe8c6ff9ac20d1126fe6f81d253dc87206","tid":1183202,"uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:59:23.000Z","msg":"小弟新手想入手一個攝影背把，目前只考慮會帶一機（連鏡）+1鏡（唔會係大炮），因為之前有淘寶用過啲背包太重，重頭送左比人<br />\n依家心目中有幾個選擇請指教下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinktankphoto.com/collections/photocross-15/products/photocross-15-backpack\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinktankphoto.com%2Fcollections%2Fphotocross-15%2Fproducts%2Fphotocross-15-backpack&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=20bbb19d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinktankphoto.com/collections/photocross-15/products/photocross-15-backpack</a><br />\n這個其實幾合心水，無論重量同外型都可以，但外型較普通，好像在港澳較難找到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thinktankphoto.com/collections/sidepath/products/sidepath\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinktankphoto.com%2Fcollections%2Fsidepath%2Fproducts%2Fsidepath&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=d130e534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinktankphoto.com/collections/sidepath/products/sidepath</a><br />\n這個更輕，當然內容物更少，遍向行山類型，可能只能一機一鏡，在官網看已沒有灰色了，也較便宜<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lowepro.com/global/freeline-bp-350-aw-black-lp37170-pww/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lowepro.com%2Fglobal%2Ffreeline-bp-350-aw-black-lp37170-pww%2F&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=257c5852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lowepro.com/global/freeline-bp-350-aw-black-lp37170-pww/</a><br />\n比起上面幾個這個較出名，也較合面，其實外型及功能都很全面，但略嫌背包較重..好處是香港較出名，不用特別找商店都有，而且dcfever 在做特價<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打請問有建議嗎？<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"4f77751ba53d6f116c97e27f211a0b09b8f84c88","tid":1183202,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5e0c9d9febf01170b09a1831ba85d0df2ef7c41","tid":1183202,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"Lowepro 果個真係去旅行先裝得滿個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f35b48596f3f6222ece4052f38dfe5bb53b9ae","tid":1183202,"uid":176924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"如果一機一鏡，lowepro果個ok"},{"pid":"43e4b5647eca782de8b9ccfc1e0a901e07f349bf","tid":1183202,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8d0dc4af23143460305537fcddb7c9f83343681d","tid":1183202,"uid":196211,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係背包"},{"pid":"e74ea7bbc931077b79c0c33977cd6d18f9647806","tid":1183202,"uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f77751ba53d6f116c97e27f211a0b09b8f84c88","tid":1183202,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"Sony 邊款呀？"},{"pid":"8200ccda8e0f3b00323bff5eb8f860bb9658f69c","tid":1183202,"uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5e0c9d9febf01170b09a1831ba85d0df2ef7c41","tid":1183202,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"Lowepro 果個真係去旅行先裝得滿個袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"除左重量之外其實我覺得唔錯"},{"pid":"41deca28aee11217c27c7c768f55243b3255d227","tid":1183202,"uid":156072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e4b5647eca782de8b9ccfc1e0a901e07f349bf","tid":1183202,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4f35b48596f3f6222ece4052f38dfe5bb53b9ae","tid":1183202,"uid":176924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"